handicraft /ˈhændɪˌkrɑːft/

(handicrafts) 

1. N-COUNT Handicrafts are activities such as embroidery and pottery which involve making things with your hands in a skilful way. 手工艺 [usu pl] 

2. N-COUNT Handicrafts are the objects that are produced by people doing handicrafts. 手工艺品 [usu pl] 

例： She sells handicrafts to the tourists. 她向游客们出售手工艺品。

